Karla Tamburrelli https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karla_Tamburrelli 0 Karla Tamburrelli is an American actress and television producer known for her work in the television series The Big Easy. In 1993, she was awarded the Joseph Jefferson Award for Best Lead Actress for "Lost in Yonkers" at the Fox Theatre in Chicago, Illinois.
